releases.name: v0.1.0
releases.description:
**`en_us`**
- Support and enabled by default: EULA auto-agree and Rcon auto-set
> If the TCP port is already in use, a random port available will be used instead
- Support i18n for English and Chinese Simplified

---

**`zh_cn`**
- 默认启用并支持自动同意EULA和自动设置Rcon
> 若TCP端口被占用会自动换一个随机的可用端口
- 支持多语言包括英语和简体中文

---

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Mooling0602/InitServer-MCDR/commits/0.1.0

description.en_us: Init your Minecraft server with MCDReforged quickly.
description.zh_cn: 在MCDR下快速初始化你的MC服务器。
